@startuml seq-stream-delivery
title Media Stream Delivery Flow

actor Child
participant "Next.js PWA" as App
participant "MediaController" as API
participant "StorageService" as Storage
participant "CDN" as CDN
participant "MinIO" as MinIO

Child -> App: Tap play on content
App -> API: GET /media/{contentId}/stream

alt Production (CDN enabled)
  API -> API: resolve CDN base URL
  API --> App: {manifestUrl: cdn.example.com/…/master.m3u8}
  App -> CDN: GET master.m3u8
  CDN -> MinIO: origin pull (cache miss)
  CDN --> App: HLS master manifest
  App -> CDN: GET quality variant playlist
  CDN --> App: segment list
  App -> CDN: GET .ts segments (adaptive bitrate)
  CDN --> App: video segments
else Development (direct MinIO)
  API -> Storage: generatePresignedGet(transcoded bucket)
  Storage -> MinIO: createPresignedGet()
  Storage --> API: presigned manifest URL
  API --> App: {manifestUrl: presigned MinIO URL}
  App -> MinIO: GET master.m3u8 (presigned)
  MinIO --> App: HLS manifest + segments
end

App -> Child: Adaptive bitrate playback

@enduml
